title: Namaste Shokudou
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Indian, Beer/Wine, Nepalese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian and Nepalese food restaurant with several vegetarian choices. Vegans to inquire about dairy use. Directions: It's a few blocks north of Matsuyama Castle cable car, south of Sekijujibyoinmae station, and west of Kamiichiman station.
